^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|BTW, there is a convention I could have used if Hope played it. It is known as a support redouble. Some people play that if the auction goes, for example, 1C-P-1H-1S, a double by me is known as a "support double." It shows exactly 3 card heart support. 2H in that auction promises 4 card support. The companion convention to that is known as a support redouble. On this auction where East doubled, e.g 1C-P-1H-Double a redouble by me is a "support redouble." It is the same idea as a support double, it shows exactly 3 card heart support. So, that would have been perfect with my hand.|
