^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First of all Kerrie made a very nice pass. Although she has 11 HCP, she can see it is a misfit hand and with misfits, you take fewer tricks than your points would indicate. So, pass was very well considered. As you can see, 2H does not even make despite the 8 card fit. I probably would have opened 3H with Eddy's hand personally. But that doesn't work out well either.|
